subject: Determining which test cases are the slowest
msgSnippet: We have lots of test cases and the entire suite takes way too long to run. Does anyone know of a tool that will time the execution of each test case so we can
messageBody:
We have lots of test cases and the entire suite takes way too long to run.

Does anyone know of a tool that will time the execution of each test case so
we can start refactoring the slowest tests?


Erik
